*Monsters are documented in detail in the monsters/ directory*

## Threat Levels

### Threat 1: Minions
Weak enemies designed to be defeated easily, generating Flow for players.
**See:** [monsters/monster_types/threat_1_minions.md](../../monsters/monster_types/threat_1_minions.md)

### Threat 2: Standard
Average enemies that present a moderate challenge.
**See:** [monsters/monster_types/threat_2_standard.md](../../monsters/monster_types/threat_2_standard.md)

### Threat 3: Champions
Powerful enemies that can challenge a full party.
**See:** [monsters/monster_types/threat_3_champion.md](../../monsters/monster_types/threat_3_champion.md)

### Threat 4: Legendary
Epic enemies that serve as campaign-defining encounters.
**See:** [monsters/monster_types/threat_4_legendary.md](../../monsters/monster_types/threat_4_legendary.md)

